Inductive gentype:
[~VAR:]
  (∀Γ s τ.
     valid_ctxt Γ ∧ MEM (s,τ) Γ ⇒ gentype Γ (VAR s : term) τ {(Γ,VAR s,τ)})
[~APP:]
